Fourth associate instruments with markets.

00:04:35.969 --> 00:04:40.290
You must be able to tell which instruments
belong to the money market, like

00:04:40.290 --> 00:04:44.880
commercial paper, and which belong to
the capital market like shares and bonds.

00:04:45.150 --> 00:04:47.550
Finally, know your regulatory bodies.

00:04:47.670 --> 00:04:50.760
Understand which body governs
which part of the system

